1 (a) The term of a for–hire driver’s license is not less than 1 year and not more
2 than 3 years, as the Commission sets.
3 (b) (1) An applicant for a renewal of a for–hire driver’s license shall:
4 (I) submit to the Commission an application on the form that the
5 Commission provides; AND
